人工智能生成的虚假 Drake 和 The Weeknd 歌曲已提交格莱美考虑https://www.nme.com/news/music/fake-ai- generated-drake-and-the-weeknd-song-subscribed-for-grammy-consideration-3494646?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=fake-ai-生成的德雷克和周末歌曲提交格莱美审议Damian JonesThu, 07 Sep 2023 14:05:10 +0000 Music NewsNewsPopRap https://www.nme.com/?p=3494646 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_drake_theweeknd_getty_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="德雷克和周末" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_drake_theweeknd_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_drake_theweeknd_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_drake_theweeknd_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_drake_theweeknd_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_drake_theweeknd_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_drake_theweeknd_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> 《袖子上的心》在今年早些时候被禁之前曾一度火爆</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fake-ai-generated-drake-and-the-weeknd-song-submitted-for-grammy-consideration-3494646">提交给格莱美考虑的由 Fake AI 生成的 Drake 和 The Weeknd 歌曲</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_drake_theweeknd_getty_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="德雷克和周末" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_drake_theweeknd_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_drake_theweeknd_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_drake_theweeknd_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_drake_theweeknd_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_drake_theweeknd_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/2023_drake_theweeknd_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>由人工智能生成的、模仿<a href="/artists/drake">Drake</a>和<a href="/artists/the-weeknd">The Weeknd 的</a>人声合作项目已提交格莱美颁奖典礼审议。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/ai-music-oasis-liam-gallagher-drake-weeknd-3432529">在人工智能绿洲时代，平凡是没有意义的</a></strong></li></ul><p>这首由匿名制作人 Ghostwriter 创作和制作的歌曲《Heart On My Sleeve》在今年早些时候首次出现时，仅在 TikTok 上就在几个小时内爆红，点击量就达到了 1300 万次。</p><p>在 Apple Music、Spotify 和 Tidal 等流行的 DSP 上，这首歌也有数十万次播放—— <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/universal-music-strip-viral-ai-generated-drake-and-the-weeknd-collaboration-from-streaming-platforms-3432055">在环球音乐集团禁止这首歌之前，</a> YouTube 上的观看次数超过 100,000 次。</p><p>现在，Ghostwriter 的一位代表已向<a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/09/05/arts/music/ghostwriter-whiplash-travis-scott-21-savage.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow"><em>《纽约时报》</em></a>证实，该歌曲已提交格莱美两个类别的考虑：最佳说唱歌曲和年度歌曲 - 两者均授予歌曲作者，而不是表演者。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="und" dir="ltr">嗨，我是代笔作家。 <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/drake?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#drake</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/aivoice?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#aivoice</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/theweeknd?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#theweeknd</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/ai?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#ai</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/aidrake?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#aidrake</a> <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/theweekndai?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#theweekndai</a> <a href="https://t.co/lUUAHC1Xw8">pic.twitter.com/lUUAHC1Xw8</a></p><p> - Ghostwriter977 (@imghostwrit3r) <a href="https://twitter.com/imghostwrit3r/status/1647623877214732290?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 4 月 16 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>据唱片学院首席执行官小哈维·梅森 (Harvey Mason Jr.) 称，这首歌可能因创意而符合资格，而且它是人类创作和录制的原创作品。正因为如此，梅森补充道：“它绝对符合条件，因为它是由人类编写的。”</p><p>但提交的要求之一是该曲目必须“通过实体店、第三方在线零售商和/或流媒体服务在全国范围内销售”。</p><p>不过，由于今年早些时候的禁令，这可能会使这首歌失去提交资格。</p><p>与此同时，Ghostwriter 还预告了一项新的人工智能合作，其声音模仿<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/travis-scott">Travis Scott</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/21-savage">21 Savage</a> ，名为“Whiplash”。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">我用人工智能创作了特拉维斯·斯科特的歌曲壮举。 21 Savage……音乐的未来就在这里。下一个想要谁？ <a href="https://t.co/jFKLTzyzeT">pic.twitter.com/jFKLTzyzeT</a></p><p> - Ghostwriter977 (@imghostwrit3r) <a href="https://twitter.com/imghostwrit3r/status/1699143499159855241?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 9 月 5 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>他们还呼吁两位艺术家允许他们发行这首歌。</p><p>代笔人写道：“很明显，人们想要这首歌。如果您有兴趣允许我发布此记录，或者希望我删除此帖子，请在 Instagram 上私信我。如果你愿意把它发布出来，我会明确地将它标记为人工智能，并且我会直接向你支付版税。不管怎样，都要尊重。”</p><p>最近，人工智能受到了许多艺术家的批评<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/john-lydon-says-ai-will-ultimately-make-decisions-for-you-and-thats-very-dangerous-3475228">，包括约翰·莱登 (John Lydon)</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stereophonics">立体声</a>主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/stereophonics-kelly-jones-hits-out-at-use-of-ai-in-songwriting-3473528">凯利·琼斯 (Kelly Jones)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-cave-calls-chatgpt-and-ai-songwriting-a-grotesque-mockery-of-what-it-is-to-be-human-3381620">尼克·凯夫 (Nick Cave)，他们称 ChatGPT 和人工智能歌曲创作是“对人类的怪诞嘲弄”</a> 。</p><p>然而， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/smashing-pumpkins">Smashing Pumpkins</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billy-corgan">Billy Corgan</a>表示<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/smashing-pumpkins-billy-corgan-says-ai-will-change-music-forever-3446083">“人工智能将永远改变音乐”，</a>因为其他人可以“玩弄系统”并且“不会在地下室度过 10,000 个小时”。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fake-ai-generated-drake-and-the-weeknd-song-submitted-for-grammy-consideration-3494646">提交给格莱美考虑的由 Fake AI 生成的 Drake 和 The Weeknd 歌曲</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
